{"tid":1977921,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"新確診病例通報比官方快 新加坡衛生部報警處理","createTime":"2020-04-18T10:15:31.000Z","updateTime":"2020-04-18T10:35:24.000Z","uid":133680,"like":8,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"c7b277c7be65f0a3d311f8a1eaae0de420f6bde9","tid":1977921,"uid":133680,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-18T10:15:31.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://udn.com/news/story/120944/4500318\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fudn.com%2Fnews%2Fstory%2F120944%2F4500318&d=0xR7vGHOl893LUq1yoppelpzQI%2FFghXCkDWT3grjsfs%3D&h=0970b50e\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://udn.com/news/story/120944/4500318</a><br />\n新加坡昨天的新冠肺炎新病例數字提早約10小時走漏風聲，衛生部表示已針對此事報警，調查正在進行中。<br />\n<br />\n昨天（4月16日）出現的728起新病例是星國單日的最高紀錄，但衛生部晚上11時發文告公佈前，網上已流傳這個數字，一些社群媒體帳號甚至還報導了本地社區病例等細節。<br />\n<br />\n衛生部答覆《聯合早報》詢問時指出，衛生部得知此事件，並已報警處理。警方正在調查中。<br />\n<br />\n根據官方機密法令，非法傳播官方資料的罪名一旦成立，肇事者將面對不超過2000新元（約新台幣42,000元）罰款和不超過兩年監禁。"},{"pid":"fca983bf75459704a6110107e33ce7d0ef58720c","tid":1977921,"uid":3457,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-18T10:17:39.000Z","msg":"支那馬嬲省"},{"pid":"990a96234c2784f05cd0f0d28622a69737bf0071","tid":1977921,"uid":335434,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-18T10:19:18.000Z","msg":"Errrr..."},{"pid":"20650e6c7fa732ad9d09d9b6046dc798a6353573","tid":1977921,"uid":222140,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-18T10:20:13.000Z","msg":"Failed State"},{"pid":"71f20eff84c0d3ce10288a36caaacb9094591e9d","tid":1977921,"uid":2054,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-18T10:21:03.000Z","msg":"4ball9<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fa5edbcf28bc9b35b235ef1e677def1984ba99d8","tid":1977921,"uid":196924,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-18T10:24:13.000Z","msg":"MSMD🐒<div style=\"text-align: right;\"></div>"},{